quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  3,53,"HaawaariyaŇčko en wi'i kadi: "Joomi amen, men gom…óinii kon ko Jippin…óaa immorde e Linnjiila, men jokkii kadi Iisaa (yo o his), wa…ódu men e …ďen seedii…ďe goonga, gom…óim…ďe Ma e Nulaa…ďe Maa…óa"."
  3,54,"Yeddu…ďe …ďen e …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila fewji fii warugol Iisaa (yo o his), Alla Kadi Fewjani …ďe O Acci …ďe e majjere ma…ď…ďe, O NanndiŇčtini Iisaa e gorko goo. Ko Alla ∆Āuri Mo∆ī∆īude e fewjoo…ďe …ďen; tawde alaa …ďur…óo Mo tii…óude e fewjanngol ay…ďe Makko …ďen."
  3,55,"Alla Kadi Fewjani …ďe tuma nde O Daalannoo Iisaa (yo o his): "Hey Iisaa, Min ko Mi ∆≥ettitoowo ma hara a maayaa, Mi …ďamte …ďanndu ndun e ruuhu on ka Am, Mi Da…ónde so…ďe yeddu…ďe …ďen Mi Wo…ó…óiŇčtine …ďe, Mi Wa…óa …ďen jokku…ďe ma ka diina goonga (no e …ďen, gom…óim…ďe Muhammadu …ďen yo o his), e hoore …ďen yeddu…ďe ma haa √Ďalnde Darngal, e dow teddungal. Refti ko faade ka Am Min Tun woni ruttorde mo'on √Ďalnde Darngal, Mi √Ďaawira hakkunde mo'on goonga, kon ko laatino-…óon hi…óon luutondira e mu'un."
  3,56,"Ammaa non …ďen yeddu…ďe on goonga mi addan-…óaa …ďe,Mi Lepta …ďen …óon leptira …ďe muusu…óe ka aduna Warugol …ďe Hoyfina …ďe ekn,ka laakara kan,ko lepte yiite.Alanaa…ďe faabotoo…ďe du√Īana …ďe lepte …óen."
  3,57,"Ammaa …ďen gom…óim…ďe ma e goonga mo addan…óaa…ďe on, …ďe golle golle-mo∆ī∆īe: immorde e juulugol, jakka, hoora, e jokkere en…óam, ekn, pellet, Alla Yo…ďiray …ďe baraaji golle ma…ď…ďe …óen no timmiri; huunde …óuytetaako e mun. Ndee yeewtere fii jokku…ďe "Almasiihu" on ado Nuleede Muhammadu (on mo jam e kisiyee woni e mun on); mo Almasiihu on tigiri wewlini fii mun. Alla Yi…óaa too√Īoo…ďe …ďen, no jeyaa ko …ďuri mawnude e too√Īe, kafidugol e Alla Toowu…óo On, fenna Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen."
  3,58,"Koo ko men janngaŇčta maa e kumpite Iisaa (yo o his), immorde e aayeeje …ďaŇčngu…óe tinndinooje e sellugol kon ko Mi Jippini e Maa…óa; ko JaŇčtoore gom…óu…ďe …ďen, √Ďe√Ī√Īaande nde mehre alaa e mun."
  3,59,"Pellet tagudu Iisaa ndun (yo o his) ka Alla, no wa'i wa tagudu Aadama ndun e mbummbuldi; ko aldaa e Neene e Baaba, Alla Daalan mo tun: "Laato …ďanndiŇčke!" o laatori no Alla Toowu…óo On Faandori non. Hol no …ďe aa∆īorta wonnde ko o rewetee…óo e hoore hujja tagireede mo ko aldaa e Baaba, him…ďe jannga kadi wonnde Aadama ko …ďanndiŇčke; …óum e wonnde o tagiraama ko aldaa e Neene e Baaba?!"
  3,60,"Goonga ka sikke alaa e mu'un kan fii Iisaa (yo his), ko kan Jippinaa e maa…óa immorde e Joomi ma'a, wata a laatodu e sikkiti…ďe murtu…ďe …ďen; si ko woni, tabitu e goonga maa kan."
  3,61,"Kala wennju…óo an nulaa…óo, immorde e Annasaara en, e fiyaake Iisaa, aa∆īii…óo wonnde on wanaa jeyaa…óo Alla; …ďaawo kon ko aru-maa e ganndal sellungal fii makko, maakaŇč…ďe: "Aree nodden ko tawdee, …ďi…ó…ďe amen e …ďi…ó…ďe mo'on, rew…ďe amen e rew…ďe mo'on, ko'e amen e ko'e mo'on, moo…ďondiren en fow, refti √Īaagoren Alla toraare nde O JippiŇčta kuddi Makko ndin e hoore fenoo…ďe …ďen e amen e mo'on"."